I wish to complain on behalf of Carenne Support that  
the blog http://carennegate.blogspot.com.au/. Carenne Support is an  
organisation which is set up in Bathurst, NSW, Australia to support  
students who attend Careene School in Bathurst which is school for
students  
with disability.

On the blog mentioned above there is content concerning Carenne School and
 
Carenne Support as well as its employees and contractors which we believe 

is in breach of the law of Australia and we request the removal of the
blog  
from the internet.

In particular it is my contention that the content is in breach of
numerous  
legislation as follows
Section 13 Crimes (Domestic and Personal Violence) Act 2007 (NSW)
Section 529 Crimes Act 1900 (NSW)
Privacy and Personal Information Protection Act 1998
Using a carriage service to menace, harass or cause offence s 474.17  
Criminal Code 1995 (Cth)
Health Records and Information Privacy Act 2002
